linux offer modutils tools to operate modules:
  the  modutils tool include:
insmod:install modules
    eg:insmod hello.ko (will run hello_init())
    can see log in /var/log/message or dmesg|tail
    detail insmod x.ko arg1=value1 arg2=value2.../no ,
rmmod:remove modules
   eg:rmmod hello.ko(will run hello_exit())
modprobe:a pro insmod and rmmod command can deal dependence
lsmod:can list modules that insmod
modinfl:can search modules info like author
